OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDozens take refuge in pub  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Famid heavy snowfall        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, About 40 people were forced to take    
OL,6, refuge in a pub overnight after heavy  
OL,7, snowfall forced some to abandon their  
OL,8, cars on impassable roads.              
OL,10,FThe Bear Inn, in Burwash, East Sussex, 
OL,11,Fthrew open its doors to those stranded,
OL,12,Fproviding hot drinks, log fires, and   
OL,13,Fmattresses for children.               
OL,15,FOne of those was Dr Alexandra Loske,   
OL,16,Fwho said: "Many sleeping on the floor  
OL,17,Ftonight but we are all happy."         
OL,19,FThe cold spell is set to continue, with
OL,20,Ffurther disruption possible.           
